==Arabic==
===Verb I===
'''{{ARchar|كَتَبَ}}''' (kátaba)

# to [[write]], to [[pen]], to [[write]] down, to [[inscribe]], to [[enter]], to [[record]], to [[register]]
# to [[compose]], to [[draw]] up, to [[draft]]
# to [[bequeath]]
# to [[prescribe]]
# to [[foreordain]], to [[destine]]

===Verb II===
'''{{ARchar|كَتّبَ}}''' (káttaba) ''(causative)''

# to cause to [[write]], to make someone write
# to [[deploy]] in [[squadron]]s

===Verb III===
'''{{ARchar|كَاتَبَ}}''' (ká:taba) ''([[conative]])''

# to keep up a [[correspondence]], to [[correspond]] with

===Verb IV===
'''{{ARchar|أكتَبَ}}''' (’áktaba) ''(causative)''

# to [[dictate]] something to, to make someone [[write]]

===Verb VI===
'''{{ARchar|تَكَاتَبَ}}''' (taká:taba) ''(reciprocal)''

# to [[write]] to each other

===Verb VII===
'''{{ARchar|اِنكَتَبَ}}''' (inkátaba) ''(reflexive)''

# to [[subscribe]]

===Verb VIII===
'''{{ARchar|اِكتَتَبَ}}''' (iktátaba) ''(reflexive, passive)''

# to [[write]] something
# to [[copy]] something, to make a copy
# to enter one’s name
# to [[subscribe]]
# to [[contribute]] (money)
# to be entered, recorded, registered

===Verb X===
'''{{ARchar|اِستَكتَبَ}}''' (istáktaba)

# to ask someone to [[write]]
# to [[dictate]]
# to have someone [[write]]
# to have a copy made

===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|كُتُب}}''' (kútub) (''plural of'' {{ARchar|[[كتاب]]}})

# pieces of [[writing]], [[record]]s, [[paper]]s
# [[letter]]s, [[note]]s, [[message]]s
# [[document]]s, [[deed]], [[contract]]s
# [[book]]s

